description: Test function for checking fees and processes related to trading size numbers

parameters.name: service_id
parameters.description: Unique ID related to each request

parameters.name: broker_token
parameters.description: Token for MT4/MT5 query, using to identify fund permission to the api query process

parameters.name: mt_type
parameters.description: The platform identifier to protect api call ends. Available values: mt4, mt5

parameters.name: margin
parameters.description: Used for test to identify free margin used to open order

parameters.name: order_lot
parameters.description: The lot in order. You can specify up to 10 decimal places like 0.01234567891

parameters.name: user_id
parameters.description: Uniquely unique identifier for an order

parameters.name: symbol_name_short
parameters.description: The symbol to look for process and test action
